Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:29.75,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fad(100,250)}四月28日 Eternidate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.51,0:01:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說過了你應該休息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么不肯聽別人的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發熱是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你不一樣 我一直是個hot的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉好奇怪 好hot啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四月28日 Michiko病倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#12 煉獄108度電波
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fad(50,250)}四月29日 日出飯店
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你母親生病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你母親吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多大了？ 10歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過長大后就會變得扭曲、丑陋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是會那樣的孩子 真羨慕你母親
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做旅行是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實阿姨我也是旅行者 雖然是獨自一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中的要困難很多啊 你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白吧 真的是很孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 水龍頭不可以一直開著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 有事情的話可以找我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只吃藥的話要花多少天才會好啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖的越久住宿費越多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 只有逃跑了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那邊的話有花27Arca就可住下的宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我可以做的工作 我什么都愿意干
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給這個號碼打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個簡單的工作 收入也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 沒有身份證也可以去的醫院有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話不要太貴 但是醫術高明的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決對不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搞得像個小孩子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去的話 能治好的病也好不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病已經好了 精神十足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已經是成年人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去你一個人去 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太孩子氣了 Orz
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配這個宇宙的法則你們知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是原因和結果的因果律
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是能夠打破因果律的唯一的神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.28,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人們稱我為Deus(葡語：神)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到銀河系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由神親自操刀的話 什么病都會瞬間消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回去 但是我只能找到這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gerson
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備手術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿意度120% 奇跡般的Show Time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想對我注射這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們坐超特快列車下地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是普通的麻醉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gerson 給我按好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是無 無的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang（宇宙誕生的大爆炸）!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擴張的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光芒照亮黑暗的銀河系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太陽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開天辟地！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼霧喚雨 化為海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大地出現 動物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.42,0:06:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后我創造了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿是缺陷的失敗之作 你聽的到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是生命的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像變好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個醫生好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就是一切的元兇 你可以安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是神技 Magic Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是病歷和賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 和之前說的價格不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附加治療 另外付費？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那么多錢 而且事前我也沒聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在你聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能這樣... 我無法認同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在懷疑Deus我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是幸福的傳道士 一次都沒有覺得自己是神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次都沒有過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是... 你!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gerson...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Amigo(葡語：朋友)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是的你Amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到這個份上你還不相信的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的努力就付諸東流了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家伙的病也永遠不會好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢的話 我今晚會去打工 明天一定付
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信Deus了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.22,0:08:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的承諾要用書面形式記錄下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像坐超特快列車下地獄的只有我一個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死嗎 臭小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼在看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}荒野農場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這惱人的滾動廣告條這片還真愛上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的山賊來了的話 就大聲呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 別讓他們逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以借用電話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fad(250,100)}四月30日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意志還比不上狗啊 錢不能給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想給你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個你想拿多少就拿多少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 Bud
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 明天 明天是不會平等地出現在每個人的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在規定日期內未能支付費用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每超過1日 作為利息收取雙倍費用 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈有此理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有寫過這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是你寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的字才沒有這么難看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去警察局嗎 Amigo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無所謂 求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被盤問起來的話 就不只是一點小問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒一點沒有退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么要喝這種東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喉嚨痛 喝一點會舒服些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以喝了一點點...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 我聽不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為喝這種東西 病才沒有好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白！ 完全不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我虛弱的時候 對我溫柔點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.68,0:12:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進 請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然賣相不好 不過看起來很好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我有個請求...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺什么事情都會順利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Hiroshi啊 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}還在做花癡夢吶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山賊們今晚會來 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清晰的第六感是這樣告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你女兒的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是某人要的氣味樣本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么這個是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫給我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}給我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feliciano剛剛被人甩了 完全地受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會走掉的 Feliciano
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個女博士歡好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女...博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的葡萄酒很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭生啤？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}暗示不帶安全套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的 你一定會沉迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.53,0:14:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒點風險也值得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個適合我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜猜看我內褲的顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭被束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.89,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kimono穿起來松松的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的哦 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從和你相識開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想過 說不定你...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 Hiroshi 我現在就去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭生啤？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的 你一定會沉迷的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開 我好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會走掉的 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那個女博士歡好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.59,0:16:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么... 回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bang！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些家伙對我下了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終于墮落成山賊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bud
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走投無路了...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有帶你的母親去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:18:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 去了一個叫Deus的人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 那個家伙不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鎮上沒有人不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先是地下醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后來為了還賭債才開始搞那個心靈手術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈手術？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不用手術刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝成從體內取出病巢的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實什么也不是 三流的魔術表演
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是把事先藏好的東西給人看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的口頭禪 “不愧是神技 Magic Hand”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.75,0:18:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有人搭理他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我是傻瓜 大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是神的話 我就要化為惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}レ…ハナ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先給我跪下 Deus！ 談事情在這之后！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus！ 給我滾出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.11,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deus在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開對我下的詛咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下詛咒的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 完全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是詛咒 詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是什么表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你和他們串通起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.76,0:19:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手里的鐵棒是怎么回事 想揍我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 我才不怕你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球在運動 世界在轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要生氣 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前的行為非常野蠻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fad(200,50)}四月31日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還是去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天隔壁的阿姨會帶我們去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些 被砸壞的電視機是個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3}待續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:22.99,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}追いかけて　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:22.99,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}追赶着 追赶着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.03,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}零れそうな星の降る夜に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:33.03,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}在摇摇欲坠的星星落下的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.21,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}信じたくなる起こらない奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:36.21,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}相信会发生却没有发生的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:42.41,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}僕とあいつの真ん中にいつも居た 君の横顔をずっと見ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:42.41,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}我一直注视着总是处在我和他之间的你的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:45.08,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}君のすぐ隣のBest Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:45.08,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}我是你近在咫尺的Best Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.75,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}僕の胸に仕舞い込んだ本音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.75,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}埋藏于我心间的真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:52.67,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}もし今ここで伝えたら　この世界は姿を変えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:52.67,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}如果现在就在这里传达的话 这个世界的样貌会改变吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:58.25,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}神様は信じないだけど　星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:58.25,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}虽然我不相信神 但是还是向星星许了愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:04.45,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}もう君に会いたくて　眠れない夜思いを募る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.41,0:22:04.45,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}太想见你 无眠的夜晚累积着对你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.47,0:22:06.79,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a2}Baby I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:17.86,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}寂しさを　切なさも　君と出会い　気付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:17.86,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}在与你邂逅之后才发觉寂寞、伤感的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:23.65,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7}{\fad(200,200)}いつも探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.92,0:22:23.65,lyrics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}{\fad(200,200)}一直在找寻
